  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dc5\u0daf\u0dcf \u0dad\u0dda\u0dc0\u0dcf \u0d9a\u0da7\u0dba\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dd4 \u0db8\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d85\u0dc3\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Dalada Teva activities from Malwatte to Asgiri",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The handing over of the Teva activities for the Dalai Lama at the historic Sri Dalada Palace in Kandy from Malwatu Maha Vihara to Asgiri Maha Vihara took place today (14) in the afternoon after Esala Pun Poho.",
        "Accordingly, on behalf of the Malwathu faction, who had performed Teva activities for Dalada in the last year, Sri Siddhartha Sumangala Maha Na Thero of the Malwathu faction, Mahanayake Thibbatuwe, and the Mahanayake Varakagoda Gnanarathana of the Asgiri faction, who will perform Teva activities until Esala Pun Poho next year, visited the Dalada Palace. The tea transfer was done according to ancient tradition.",
        "The Maha Sangharatna in charge of Teva affairs, Mr. Pradeep Nilanga Dela of Diyawadana Nilame and other staff members involved in Teva affairs participated in this event."
      ],
